Berserker Armour

Berserkers are unrestricted martial combatants. They may wear light, medium,
or heavy armour, including shields, without disabling Berserker abilities or
combat progression. Armour material is likewise unrestricted.

Individual items may still impose their own race, level, size, slot, or other
wear restrictions. Those restrictions belong to the item rather than the
Berserker guild.

Use "berhelp armour" or "berhelp armor" to read this information again.
